message:
Hey ya'll! 
so it's a new school year which means - new people to share the Good News with!
A few of us have been 'put in charge' to start leading times this year
please take a look at the Google document to see the new sharing times
If none of these work for you but you feel compelled 'to go' PLEASE, set up a new time!
Anyone can edit this document
You can also add your name to the times already laid out
We will be starting officially next week on Monday (so everyone can get their schedules established)
If you have any questions contact me, Ella Borgenheimer, Peter Kelly, Autumn Beckman, or David Morelli

Peace n' blessings
